data.description: Every detail has been thought of on the interior and exterior of this beautiful 4-bedroom 1.5 bath home in Fairfield School District! Situated in a peaceful country setting with a large private back yard, great landscaping, 2 car garage and a 16x10 garden shed for extra storage!  New metal roof, vinyl siding, soffit, fascia, gutters, leaf guards, front door and garage windows were installed in 2023. Inside you will find a lovely eat in kitchen with refinished cabinets and new laminate flooring updated in 2023. The bedrooms have newer carpet and great closet space and both bathrooms have been recently remodeled as well. Furnace was replaced in 2018, new water softener in 2019, new central air unit installed in 2021, well pump & tank was replaced in 2020 AND the basement has a lifetime structural warranty transferable to the new owners. Truly all you need to do is move right in!
